To
manufacture PCBs, we use raw materials such as laminated layers of fiberglass, copper foil, chemical solutions, gold, and other commodity products, which we order from our suppliers. In the case of backplane assemblies, components include
connectors, sheet metal, capacitors, resistors and diodes, many of which are custom made and controlled by our customers&#146; approved vendors. If raw material and component prices increase, it may reduce our gross margins. 
