requirements, more extensive debarments from export privileges, or loss of authorizations needed to conduct aspects of our international business.  In certain countries, TTM may engage third-party agents or intermediaries, such as customs agents, to act on each of their behalves, and if these third-party agents or intermediaries violate applicable
